<!--
  Wazuh Rules for Iranian APT Detection - March 2026 Expansion
  Version: 1.0
  Last Updated: 2026-03-24

  This ruleset expands detection coverage for Iranian APT activities
  identified through deep research of 2025-2026 operations.

  New threat families covered:
  - MuddyViper/Fooder backdoor (MuddyWater)
  - WezRat infostealer (Cotton Sandstorm)
  - Handala/Void Manticore wiper + Stryker attack
  - Sicarii RaaS
  - WhiteLock ransomware
  - Crafty Camel/Sosano backdoor
  - SloppyMIO/RedKitten steganography
  - UNC1549 LIGHTRAIL/CRASHPAD/DCSYNCER/SIGHTGRAB
  - APT42 TAMECAT
  - IOCONTROL expanded indicators
  - BQT.Lock/Baqiyat (Hezbollah RaaS)

  Rule ID Range: 101300-101450
-->

<group name="iranian_apt,march2026_expansion,">

